OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The BBC should be "realistic about what
OL,6, it can expect people to pay" for the TV
OL,7, licence fee during times of high       
OL,8, inflation, the prime minister has said.
OL,10,FRishi Sunak said the BBC should "cut   
OL,11,Fits cloth appropriately" and welcomed  
OL,12,Fsavings it was looking to make.        
OL,14,FThe corporation said next year's cost  
OL,15,Fwas "unconfirmed" but that it had      
OL,16,Fpreviously agreed increases in line    
OL,17,Fwith inflation to start from 2024.     
OL,19,FThe PM said final decisions on the     
OL,20,Ffuture of the fee had not been made.   
